Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.12,0:19:03.87,Scr,,0,0,0,,{\bord6\3c&H652919&\1c&HF7F7FA&\fs70\pos(428,910)\frz32.5}忘带钥匙了进不去门
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.62,0:19:08.13,Scr,,0,0,0,,{\bord4\3c&HFAFAFD&\1c&H6C3929&\fs70\frz32.35\pos(1192,380)}坏了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.62,0:19:08.13,Scr,,0,0,0,,{\bord4\3c&HFAFAFD&\1c&H6C3929&\fs70\frz32.86\pos(1350,398)}差不多要两小时
